== Land of Summoned Monsters ==

Special dungeon where Rydia grew up:
* Asura boss fight
* Leviathan boss fight
* Both become summons after defeat
* Must speak to King/Queen after

== Lunar Subterrane ==

Bahamut is found here:
* Requires defeating previous Bahamut encounter
* Most powerful summon in the game
* High MP cost

